@host = https://localhost:44319

### Validation - invalid company id
POST {{host}}/api/contact-persons
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "companyId": 0,
  "name": "Invalid Contact",
  "position": "Recruiter",
  "email": "test@example.com"
}

### Validation - missing name
POST {{host}}/api/contact-persons
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "companyId": 1,
  "position": "Recruiter",
  "email": "test@example.com"
}

### Validation - invalid email
POST {{host}}/api/contact-persons
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "companyId": 1,
  "name": "Invalid Email Contact",
  "position": "Recruiter",
  "email": "not-an-email"
}

### Business validation - company not found
POST {{host}}/api/contact-persons
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "companyId": 999,
  "name": "Ghost Recruiter",
  "position": "Recruiter",
  "email": "ghost@example.com"
}